  "texts": [
    "For clonogenic survival assays, stained plates were scanned and the ImageJ plugin ColonyArea was used to automatically quantify colonies 86.",
    "A threshold of 200 was manually applied to all experiments.",
    "Colony survival in treated experimental groups was normalized to untreated controls.",
    "For chemical inhibitor studies, synergy distribution heatmaps were generated by SynergyFinder web application (Version 3.0) (https://synergyfinder.fimm.fi/) 87.",
    "To quantify cells containing CFP-RAD18 nuclear foci, and co-localization of GFP-Polκ/PCNA foci, composite images acquired using a Zeiss LSM 710 microscope were generated using Fiji to overlay multiple channels."
